Uses of Class
org.anyframe.query.exception.QueryException

Packages that use QueryException
org.anyframe.query Provides interface for executing SQL queries or updates, initiating iteration over ResultSets And also provides exception class that is thrown when there is any problem executing the query 
org.anyframe.query.exception   
org.anyframe.query.impl Provides implementation class for QueryService interface and also provides paging classes
